&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;Check camera devices: &lt;code&gt;ls -l /dev/video*&lt;/code&gt;
Start Network Manager: &lt;code&gt;sudo systemctl start NetworkManager&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>